rComments: Prof. was a pretty chill. The class consists of 5 assignments and 3 big tests (no exam!). Lectures get posted on his site and the class is pretty moderate. Pay attention and you'll do great. He does do attendance, so show up, on time. He's got an accent, so sometimes his lecture is a little unclear; he does repeat/clarify things if you just ask.

Average professor. Not very accessible after or before class, as he immediately runs off without waiting for many questions from his students. Asks us for feedback for his seminar course, but does not adopt any of the suggested changes. Incredibly easy A+, but a fairly humdrum course. Had to write essays that were really short stories as well?
He covers useful material and does a good job overall
